<p><a name="Further_reading" id="Further_reading"></a></p>
<h2><span class="mw-headline">Further reading</span></h2>
<ul>
<li>R. D. Ballard, F, T. Hiebert, D. F. Coleman, C. Ward, J. Smith, K. Willis, B. Foley, K. Croff, C. Major, and F. Torre, "Deepwater Archaeology of the Black Sea: The 2000 Season at Sinop, Turkey" American Journal of Archaeology Vol. 105 No. 4 (October 2001).</li>
</ul>
